cu.explanation_en: Changing the NG AMF IP address to an unreachable subnet (10.0.0.1) will prevent the CU from establishing a connection to the AMF, leading to NG interface failure and system initialization errors.

du.explanation_en: Modifying the SSB absolute frequency to 641284 misaligns it with the expected frequency grid, causing synchronization issues and potential cell search failures in UEs.
